			<h3>Audience</h3>
			<p>
				The primary audience of this tool are doctors, therapists, teachers, social workers, and other professionals that wish to screen their clients for Adverse Childhood Experiences (ACEs) with the aim of integrating the knowledge of the ACE score into their work with the client.
			</p>
			<h3>How it works</h3>
			<p>
				The ACE Toolkit is available on traditional computers, tablets, and smartphones.
			</p>
